channel.title: Necessary places to change ip in order to play online
channel.description: As the title says, I would like to know all the areas (client.java, gui.java, etc.) in server/client side where I have to change the ip to either my no-ip IP or the 1.1.1.1 ip. I am making a RSPS and I havent worked on this stuff in about 6 years so I'm very rusty. Thanks a lot.
